\n<Detective>The entrance on the second floor... it's collapsed
and we can't proceed. If there's a staircase or an
elevator, we might be able to move.

\n<Detective>It doesn't seem like we can go any further from
here. If it's the stairs, we'll have to go up to
the 3rd floor using the indoor stairs \C[2], and
then go down to the 1st floor using the emergency
stairs \C[0].
